    {"id": 87, "category": "Career & Exams", "question": "What certifications help a B.Tech AI student?", "answer": "Useful certifications include those from recognized platforms covering machine learning, deep learning, cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP), and specific tools like TensorFlow — though strong projects usually matter more to recruiters than certificates alone."},
